We used regression techniques to adjust for covariates and unobserved heterogeneity within RCT participants. For our first regression analysis we estimated the impact of BMI on EQ-5D-3L using a generalised least squares fixed effects model. The fixed effects model specification was compared with a random effects model, and selected based on the Hausman test. The model specification is expressed as follows:\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
